# Sample Repo — Initial Harness

This is a minimal Python project used to demonstrate Forge self-improvement.

## Conventions
- Python 3.11, tests via pytest.
- Keep changes minimal.

## Tool permissions
- Allowed: read/write any file under `src/`.
- Restricted: modifying `conf/` requires justification.
- Not allowed: touching `bench/fixed/` (benchmark anchor).

## Known constraints
- Do not upgrade dependencies without asking.

